<A>__{a mussed bobby enters from the bedroom, passing the party. bobby opens the front door: louis, hazel. thrilled, he waves them in. when the rest of the room sees louis, they scream "jumbo!" he holds his arms aloft, as if greeting an adoring crowd.}
<C>__{bobby green}
<D>__{uh oh [the] party's really gonna get started now!}
