<C>__{freddie}
<D>__{hey falsetti! you get what we wanted?}
<C>__{louis falsetti}
<P>__{(grinning)}
<D>__{indeed i did, my friend!}
<P>__{(quieter, to bobby)}
<D>__{see, i woulda been here sooner, `cept i hadda go across town, lose all the cops }
