<D>__{there weren't no cops following us!}
<C>__{louis falsetti}
<D>__{shut your mouth! you wouldn't recognize `em they were, they were all undercover.}
<A>__{bobby laughs happily, knowing this is bullshit. hazel shakes her head, joins the gals. louis starts emptying his pockets. out comes a pharmacy. drugs spill all over a formica endtable. louder:}
